column58: Driver of truck that rear ended Ediberto Huertas

incorrect address 2/21/18 BHP
Simba was heading South on Casey Road. When traffic slowed, Simba came to a shop. The vehicle behind her failed to slow and rear ended her. The at fault party's name is Paulette - She was cited for the rear end crash. HSCO did a report.
called & changed address 8/7/14 BHP
